                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860111-62-off284 t17860111-62-cd282"></join> last, at the parish of <placeName id="t17860111-62-crimeloc283">St. Mary Woolnorth</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17860111-62-crimeloc283" type="placeName" value="St. Mary Woolnorth"></interp>
