                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860111-62-off284 t17860111-62-crimeloc283"></join>, in the city of London, <rs id="t17860111-62-off284" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17860111-62-off284" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
